prompt.content: Let G be an undirected graph with edge set {(32,3), (16,12), (3,19), (32,34), (34,6), (6,16), (19,47), (47,28)}. Find a path from vertex 32 to vertex 12. Express your final answer in the form \boxed{v1,v2,...,vk}, where each vertex is separated by a comma.
